    {
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>query<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>: executes a query, specified by a TSQL string; the results are returned to the <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>success<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept> callback on the <bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>options<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept> object.",
