      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>queryRaw<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>: like <bpt id=\"p2\">*</bpt>query<ept id=\"p2\">*</ept> except that the result set returned from the query is in a \"raw\" format (see example below)."
    },
