      ],
      "content": "<ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;a name=\"static-query\"&gt;</ph><ph id=\"ph2\">&lt;/a&gt;</ph>How to: Run a static query"
    },
    {
      "content": "The following query has no parameters and returns three records from the <ph id=\"ph1\">`statusupdate`</ph> table.",
      "pos": [
